<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"><meta name="description" content="Portfolio of Navneet Sharma — Cloud, DevOps and AI Platform Architect."><title>Navneet Sharma | Cloud & AI Platform Architect</title></head><body>
<header><nav class="shell"><a class="brand" href="/"><span>N</span><b>Navneet Sharma</b></a><div class="navlinks"><a href="#work">Work</a><a href="#expertise">Expertise</a><a href="https://buildwithnavneet.com">Blog ↗</a></div></nav></header>
<main>
<section class="hero shell"><div><p class="eyebrow">CLOUD · DEVOPS · AI INFRASTRUCTURE</p><h1>I build the platforms<br><em>behind modern technology.</em></h1><p class="lead">I'm <strong>Navneet Sharma</strong>, a Cloud & AI Platform Architect with 12+ years of experience designing infrastructure, automation and engineering platforms that scale.</p><div class="actions"><a class="primary" href="#work">Explore my work <span>↘</span></a><a class="secondary" href="https://buildwithnavneet.com">Read my writing <span>→</span></a></div><div class="proof"><span><b>12+</b> years in technology</span><span><b>Cloud → AI</b> evolving with the industry</span><span><b>Build in public</b> sharing what I learn</span></div></div><div class="visual" aria-hidden="true"><div class="orbit one"></div><div class="orbit two"></div><div class="core">N<span>S</span></div><div class="card c1"><small>ARCHITECTURE</small><b>Systems that scale</b></div><div class="card c2"><small>PHILOSOPHY</small><b>Learn. Build. Share.</b></div></div></section>
<section id="expertise" class="section shell"><div class="heading"><div><p class="eyebrow">WHAT I WORK ON</p><h2>Engineering across the stack.</h2></div><p>I work where infrastructure, developer experience and emerging AI systems meet.</p></div><div class="grid">{expertise.map(([title,text,tags])=><article class="expert"><span class="plus">+</span><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p><small>{tags}</small></article>)}</div></section>
<section id="work" class="work"><div class="shell"><div class="heading light"><div><p class="eyebrow">SELECTED WORK</p><h2>Portfolio & case studies.</h2></div><p>Architecture, automation and platform projects focused on solving real engineering problems.</p></div><div class="grid">{projects.map(([num,title,text,tags])=><article class="project"><div class="projecttop"><span>{num}</span><small>CASE STUDY</small></div><div class="art">{num}</div><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p><small>{tags}</small></article>)}</div><p class="note">More case studies coming as I document the systems I've built and the lessons behind them.</p></div></section>
<section class="about shell"><p class="eyebrow">ABOUT</p><div><h2>Learning the future<br>by <em>building it.</em></h2><p>For more than a decade, I've worked across cloud infrastructure, DevOps and platform engineering. Today I'm extending that foundation into AI infrastructure and MLOps — while documenting the journey at BuildWithNavneet.</p></div><a href="https://buildwithnavneet.com">Visit BuildWithNavneet →</a></section>
</main><footer class="shell"><span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Navneet Sharma</span><span>Cloud · DevOps · AI Infrastructure</span></footer>
